(42, 13, 16, 42, 19, 9, 9, 'daughter of Abraham', 'Connection of Abraham''s Children', 'Both passages emphasize the identity of individuals as ''sons of Abraham,'' highlighting their inclusion in God''s covenant. This connection underscores the theme of deliverance and salvation for those bound or lost.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 13, 16, 55, 2, 26, 26, 'whom Satan hath bound', 'Bondage and Deliverance Theme', 'This connection highlights the theme of being bound and the need for deliverance. Both passages refer to individuals being held captive by Satan and the importance of liberation from such bondage.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
